Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.92,0:28:19.62,English,,0,0,0,,and then there has to be a way to trim that image. So, um, there has to be a way to trim that image.\N{\rChinese}呃，先裁剪那幅图，然后再有办法把那幅图裁剪一下
