Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.38,0:28:30.72,English,,0,0,0,,Um, around the world. The problem is, the problem was\N{\rChinese}呃，全球范围内。问题是，问题在于
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.72,0:28:32.58,English,,0,0,0,,that at that time the CIA didn't have a global network.\N{\rChinese}那时美国中央情报局还没有全球网络。
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.80,0:28:35.86,English,,0,0,0,,The Vatican did have a global intelligence network and\N{\rChinese}梵蒂克确实拥有全球情报网络。
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.86,0:28:40.16,English,,0,0,0,,so the CIA and the Vatican formed a holy alliance against communism.\N{\rChinese}于是美国中央情报局与梵蒂克结成了对抗共的圣盟。
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.70,0:28:43.98,English,,0,0,0,,And there have been\N{\rChinese}随后出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.98,0:28:46.44,English,,0,0,0,,so many CIA directors who are Catholic\N{\rChinese}许多中央情报局局长都是天主教徒。
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.44,0:28:47.68,English,,0,0,0,,that\N{\rChinese}那时美国中央情报局被称为“行动中的天主”或“天主情报局”。
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.68,0:28:53.10,English,,0,0,0,,the CIA has been nicknamed Catholics in Action or the Catholic Intelligence Agency.\N{\rChinese}好的，梵蒂克与美国中央情报局关系非常紧密。
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.58,0:28:58.26,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, so the Vatican and the CIA are very very close.\N{\rChinese}Okay, so the Vatican and the CIA are very very close.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.80,0:29:02.32,English,,0,0,0,,Another sign is that\N{\rChinese}另一个迹象是
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.32,0:29:07.42,English,,0,0,0,,the Catholic religion is growing very very fast in America.\N{\rChinese}天主教在美国迅速增长。
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.58,0:29:10.76,English,,0,0,0,,Right now it's about 22% of the American population\N{\rChinese}目前约占美国人口的22%。
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.76,0:29:13.62,English,,0,0,0,,but all those immigrants\N{\rChinese}但所有这些移民
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.62,0:29:16.94,English,,0,0,0,,that are coming to America, half of them are Catholic\N{\rChinese}他们来到美国，半数是天主教徒
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.94,0:29:18.46,English,,0,0,0,,and these are the legal immigrants.\N{\rChinese}而这些是合法移民
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.60,0:29:21.18,English,,0,0,0,,We're not counting the illegal immigrants who are majority Catholic.\N{\rChinese}我们没有算上多数为天主教徒的非法移民。
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.48,0:29:22.64,English,,0,0,0,,And also, remember,\N{\rChinese}另外，记住，
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.68,0:29:26.32,English,,0,0,0,,Catholics have more\N{\rChinese}天主教徒有更多
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.32,0:29:30.22,English,,0,0,0,,children than Protestant families. So\N{\rChinese}孩子比新教家庭多。于是
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.22,0:29:33.42,English,,0,0,0,,the demographic trend looks\N{\rChinese}人口趋势看起来
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.42,0:29:38.32,English,,0,0,0,,very good for the Catholic faith.\N{\rChinese}对天主教派非常有利。
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.62,0:29:41.32,English,,0,0,0,,But we can also argue that\N{\rChinese}但我们也可以说，
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.32,0:29:45.14,English,,0,0,0,,if there is American Civil War, a second Civil War,\N{\rChinese}如果出现美国内战，第二场内战，
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.28,0:29:47.50,English,,0,0,0,,and the institutions of authority are destroyed,\N{\rChinese}权力机构被摧毁。
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.80,0:29:52.66,English,,0,0,0,,the American Catholics are in the best position to be able to do anything.\N{\rChinese}美国天主教徒处于最佳位置，能够做任何事。
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.66,0:29:53.94,English,,0,0,0,,So they can't be able to capture the American state.\N{\rChinese}于是他们就能掌握美国国家。
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.32,0:29:58.74,English,,0,0,0,,And if they are able to capture the American state then they would control the world.\N{\rChinese}若他们能掌握美国国家，则可统领世界。
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.12,0:30:03.48,English,,0,0,0,,So I think there are some fanatics within the Catholic Church\N{\rChinese}于是我认为天主教会内部有些狂热者
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.48,0:30:04.76,English,,0,0,0,,who\N{\rChinese}他们
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.76,0:30:08.22,English,,0,0,0,,want to initiate a second American Civil War\N{\rChinese}想要发动第二场美国内战
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.22,0:30:10.36,English,,0,0,0,,because they believe that\N{\rChinese}因为他们认为
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.36,0:30:16.08,English,,0,0,0,,this war will create the opportunity for the Catholic Church to control America\N{\rChinese}这场战争将为天主教会掌控美国创造机会
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.08,0:30:19.42,English,,0,0,0,,and thus destroy all three of its major opponents.\N{\rChinese}并因此消灭其三大对手
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.62,0:30:22.64,English,,0,0,0,,The Anglo -American empire, the nation state, and\N{\rChinese}英美帝国、民族国家与克鲁萨德的克鲁萨德国家以及现代性本身。
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.64,0:30:25.94,English,,0,0,0,,the Crusaders' Crusaders' state and modernity itself.\N{\rChinese}好了，先看了主要的末世论传统，接下来……
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.80,0:30:30.94,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, so having looked at the major eschatological traditions,\N{\rChinese}Okay, so having looked at the major eschatological traditions,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.20,0:30:33.34,English,,0,0,0,,I'm going to discuss where they converge.\N{\rChinese}我将讨论它们的汇聚点。
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.78,0:30:38.80,English,,0,0,0,,And what's really interesting is there's actually quite a few convergence points\N{\rChinese}而且真正有趣的是，实际上有不少汇聚点，且都很重要。
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.80,0:30:42.02,English,,0,0,0,,that are very important. The first convergence point is\N{\rChinese}第一个汇聚点是
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.02,0:30:45.92,English,,0,0,0,,that there will be a major conflict in the Middle East\N{\rChinese}有一场大冲突将在中东爆发
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.92,0:30:49.72,English,,0,0,0,,that will suck in the whole world.\N{\rChinese}它将把全世界卷入其中
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.78,0:30:50.98,English,,0,0,0,,It will be World War III, okay?\N{\rChinese}这将是第三次世界大战，明白吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.30,0:30:53.44,English,,0,0,0,,Second convergence point is that\N{\rChinese}第二个汇聚点是
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.44,0:30:57.46,English,,0,0,0,,America will not be involved in this war.\N{\rChinese}美国将不参与这场战争。
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.60,0:31:00.70,English,,0,0,0,,And that's very interesting because America is right now the global hegemon.\N{\rChinese}而且这很有趣，因为美国正是全球霸权。
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.02,0:31:04.00,English,,0,0,0,,So why America isn't involved in this war?\N{\rChinese}那么美国为什么没参与这场战争？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.14,0:31:07.02,English,,0,0,0,,We don't know. It could be because they launched a grunt invasion of Iran.\N{\rChinese}我们不知道。可能是因为他们发动了对伊朗的突击入侵。
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.20,0:31:09.00,English,,0,0,0,,It failed and they were forced to retreat.\N{\rChinese}入侵失败后他们被迫撤退。
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.26,0:31:12.26,English,,0,0,0,,It could be the Civil War going on in America, okay?\N{\rChinese}它可能是美国正在进行的内战，好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.36,0:31:14.30,English,,0,0,0,,But America is not involved in this war.\N{\rChinese}但美国并未参与这场战争。
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.80,0:31:16.64,English,,0,0,0,,The third convergent point is that\N{\rChinese}第三个汇聚点是
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.64,0:31:20.08,English,,0,0,0,,China is not involved in this war either.\N{\rChinese}中国也没有参与这场战争。
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.42,0:31:22.12,English,,0,0,0,,And I suspected that China has been involved in this war for days.\N{\rChinese}我猜想中国已经参与这场战争好几天了。
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.12,0:31:26.12,English,,0,0,0,,China has been involved that it's because China is facing an ecological catastrophe.\N{\rChinese}中国之所以参与是因为它正面临生态灾难。
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.50,0:31:28.42,English,,0,0,0,,It doesn't have enough water, it doesn't have enough food,\N{\rChinese}它没有足够的水，没有足够的食物，
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.52,0:31:33.88,English,,0,0,0,,it doesn't have enough resources for its people\N{\rChinese}它没有足够的资源供其人民使用，
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.88,0:31:36.28,English,,0,0,0,,and you have internal dissent throughout the nation.\N{\rChinese}并且全国各地都有内部纷争。
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.44,0:31:40.20,English,,0,0,0,,China is having a hard time keeping itself together.\N{\rChinese}中国正艰难维持统一。
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.26,0:31:46.26,English,,0,0,0,,The fourth convergence point is\N{\rChinese}第四个汇聚点是
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.26,0:31:47.56,English,,0,0,0,,that\N{\rChinese}那是……
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.56,0:31:51.90,English,,0,0,0,,the Antichrist will emerge\N{\rChinese}反基督将出现
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.90,0:31:55.94,English,,0,0,0,,and different traditions understand the Antichrist differently\N{\rChinese}不同传统对反基督的理解各异
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.94,0:31:58.46,English,,0,0,0,,but they all believe that\N{\rChinese}但他们都相信
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.46,0:32:01.62,English,,0,0,0,,this powerful force will emerge who\N{\rChinese}这股强大力量将出现，拥有魅力的领袖
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.62,0:32:02.94,English,,0,0,0,,is charismatic and who\N{\rChinese}他将统一世界。
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.94,0:32:06.68,English,,0,0,0,,will unify the world.\N{\rChinese}will unify the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.78,0:32:10.90,English,,0,0,0,,Another convergence point is that\N{\rChinese}另一个汇聚点是
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.90,0:32:15.48,English,,0,0,0,,Israel will become the dominant power in the Middle East.\N{\rChinese}以色列将成为中东的主导力量。
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.48,0:32:19.08,English,,0,0,0,,Presumably after America leaves the Middle East\N{\rChinese}大概在美国离开中东之后。
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.08,0:32:21.98,English,,0,0,0,,and we can understand why because America leaves the Middle East\N{\rChinese}于是我们可以明白原因，因为美国离开中东
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.98,0:32:23.92,English,,0,0,0,,then all of America's military infrastructure,\N{\rChinese}随后美国的全部军工设施，
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.28,0:32:26.82,English,,0,0,0,,CENTCOM, will merge with the Greater Israel Project,\N{\rChinese}CENTCOM将与大以色列计划合并
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.16,0:32:29.28,English,,0,0,0,,thus creating the Israel Empire.\N{\rChinese}于是形成了以色列帝国。
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.86,0:32:32.68,English,,0,0,0,,Another convergence point is that\N{\rChinese}另一个汇聚点是
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.66,0:32:39.56,English,,0,0,0,,anti -semitism will grow around the world compelling Jews to return to Israel.\N{\rChinese}反犹太主义将在全球蔓延，迫使犹太人归回以色列。
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.08,0:32:43.36,English,,0,0,0,,Another convergence point is\N{\rChinese}另一个汇聚点是
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.36,0:32:46.32,English,,0,0,0,,that the Dome of the Rock will be destroyed and\N{\rChinese}岩顶会被摧毁，随后...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.32,0:32:50.82,English,,0,0,0,,thus provoking the Muslim world to take arms against Israel\N{\rChinese}于是穆斯林世界会动手举兵对抗以色列。
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.82,0:32:54.00,English,,0,0,0,,and possibly initiating the war of Gog\N{\rChinese}并可能引发古古与玛古的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.00,0:32:55.78,English,,0,0,0,,and Magog.\N{\rChinese}另一个汇聚点是动荡期。
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.46,0:32:59.82,English,,0,0,0,,Another convergence point is the Age of Tribulation\N{\rChinese}另一个汇聚点是动荡期。
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.82,0:33:02.86,English,,0,0,0,,when the world will face economic,\N{\rChinese}当世界面临经济，
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.24,0:33:08.02,English,,0,0,0,,ecological, geopolitical catastrophe after catastrophe after catastrophe\N{\rChinese}生态、地缘政治灾难后又灾难后又灾难
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.02,0:33:10.46,English,,0,0,0,,when people's faith will be tested.\N{\rChinese}当人们的信仰受到考验时
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.58,0:33:15.16,English,,0,0,0,,When the Antichrist will emerge to deceive people into believing that the Antichrist will emerge to deceive people into believing that the Antichrist will\N{\rChinese}当弥撒者出现，欺骗人们相信弥撒者出现，欺骗人们相信弥撒者出现，弥撒者出现，
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.68,0:33:18.72,English,,0,0,0,,rise to deceive people into believing that\N{\rChinese}升起欺骗人们相信
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.72,0:33:20.74,English,,0,0,0,,the Antichrist will rise to deceive people Antichrist will rise to deceive people into believing that the Antichrist will rise to deceive people into believing that\N{\rChinese}弥撒者将升起欺骗人们相信弥撒者将升起欺骗人们相信那样
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.74,0:33:23.78,English,,0,0,0,,the Antichrist will rise to deceive people into denying the lie\N{\rChinese}弥撒者将升起欺骗人们以否认谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.78,0:33:27.92,English,,0,0,0,,and lie to deceive people into denying the lie and lie to deceive people into denying lie and lie to deceive people into denying the lie and lie to deceive people into denying lie and lie to deceive people into denying the lie and\N{\rChinese}又说谎以欺骗人们否认谎言，又说谎以欺骗人们否认谎言，又说谎以欺骗人们否认谎言，又说谎以欺骗人们否认谎言，又说谎以欺骗人们否认谎言，
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.92,0:33:31.54,English,,0,0,0,,lie to deceive people into denying lie and lie to deceive people into denying the lie and lie to deceive people into denying\N{\rChinese}说谎以欺骗人们否认谎言，说谎以欺骗人们否认谎言，说谎以欺骗人们否认
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.04,0:33:36.08,English,,0,0,0,,lie and lie to deceive people into denying the lie\N{\rChinese}说谎以欺骗人们否认谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.08,0:33:40.06,English,,0,0,0,,and lie to deceive people into denying lie and lie to deceive people into denying the lie\N{\rChinese}又说谎以欺骗人们否认谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.06,0:33:45.34,English,,0,0,0,,and lie to deceive people into denying in the future\N{\rChinese}又说谎以欺骗人们在未来否认
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.34,0:33:47.00,English,,0,0,0,,and what it looks like. And\N{\rChinese}以及它的样子。
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.00,0:33:51.02,English,,0,0,0,,some of these will not work out,\N{\rChinese}有些会落空
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.12,0:33:52.72,English,,0,0,0,,some of these will work out. But\N{\rChinese}有些会成功
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.72,0:33:54.72,English,,0,0,0,,it's an interesting framework for us to\N{\rChinese}这是一种有趣的框架，供我们思考地缘政治未来十到二十年可能的发展。
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.72,0:34:00.32,English,,0,0,0,,think about how geopolitics might develop over the next 10 to 20 years.\N{\rChinese}于是美国发动了对伊朗的地面入侵。
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.18,0:34:07.76,English,,0,0,0,,So the United States launched a ground invasion of Iran.\N{\rChinese}So the United States launched a ground invasion of Iran.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.00,0:34:10.00,English,,0,0,0,,Iran is supported heavily by Russia.\N{\rChinese}伊朗得到俄罗斯的大力支持。
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.00,0:34:11.64,English,,0,0,0,,The United States,\N{\rChinese}美国，
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.70,0:34:14.80,English,,0,0,0,,after a few years of fighting,\N{\rChinese}经过数年的战斗后，
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.06,0:34:16.96,English,,0,0,0,,they give up and they retreat.\N{\rChinese}他们投降并撤退。
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.80,0:34:23.06,English,,0,0,0,,And so the American Empire retreats back into the Western continent.\N{\rChinese}于是美帝国撤回西方大洲。
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.26,0:34:27.18,English,,0,0,0,,But this triggers a civil war in America.\N{\rChinese}这导致美国内战爆发。
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.08,0:34:34.66,English,,0,0,0,,In Ukraine, NATO decides Odessa will be the last step.\N{\rChinese}在乌克兰，北约决定奥德萨是最后一步。
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.14,0:34:39.44,English,,0,0,0,,So Russia encircles Odessa.\N{\rChinese}于是俄国包围奥德萨。
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.16,0:34:41.56,English,,0,0,0,,And lays siege to it.\N{\rChinese}并对其展开围攻。
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.94,0:34:45.00,English,,0,0,0,,All of NATO is brought in to defend Odessa.\N{\rChinese}所有北约成员国都被调入去保卫奥德萨。
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.22,0:34:46.52,English,,0,0,0,,This is the very last step.\N{\rChinese}这就是最后一步。
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.06,0:34:49.52,English,,0,0,0,,And France,\N{\rChinese}法国也加入了。
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.90,0:34:51.78,English,,0,0,0,,Britain, Romania, Poland,\N{\rChinese}英国、罗马尼亚、波兰，所有北约成员国都被调入。
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.60,0:34:54.46,English,,0,0,0,,all the NATO countries are brought in.\N{\rChinese}土耳其也被调入。
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.56,0:34:55.76,English,,0,0,0,,Turkey is brought in as well.\N{\rChinese}Turkey is brought in as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.44,0:34:59.02,English,,0,0,0,,And it's a stalemate.\N{\rChinese}并且是僵局。
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.48,0:35:01.70,English,,0,0,0,,This war is going nowhere. But\N{\rChinese}这场战争无进展。但
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.70,0:35:07.30,English,,0,0,0,,the Europeans don't understand why they're fighting this war.\N{\rChinese}欧洲人不明白为何要打这场战。
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.40,0:35:09.12,English,,0,0,0,,The European people revolt.\N{\rChinese}欧洲人民起义。
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.44,0:35:13.00,English,,0,0,0,,And this is a stalemate. This causes civil war in France, in Britain.\N{\rChinese}而这又是僵局。于是法国、英国爆发内战。
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.14,0:35:15.76,English,,0,0,0,,It causes political upheaval in Germany.\N{\rChinese}它导致德国政治动荡。
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.90,0:35:19.30,English,,0,0,0,,It causes a political revolution in Turkey.\N{\rChinese}它导致土耳其政治革命。
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.68,0:35:22.88,English,,0,0,0,,And after these civil wars\N{\rChinese}而在这些内战之后
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.88,0:35:27.54,English,,0,0,0,,and these revolutions, Europe becomes more pro -Russian.\N{\rChinese}以及这些革命后，欧洲变得更亲俄
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.74,0:35:31.18,English,,0,0,0,,Allowing for reconciliation between Putin\N{\rChinese}为普京与欧洲的和解提供可能。
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.18,0:35:33.08,English,,0,0,0,,and Europe.\N{\rChinese}and Europe.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.26,0:35:34.98,English,,0,0,0,,Turkey is destroyed in this process.\N{\rChinese}土耳其在此过程中被摧毁。
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.98,0:35:39.38,English,,0,0,0,,Putin allows the Greeks to return to Constantinople.\N{\rChinese}普京允许希腊人返回君士坦丁堡。
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.38,0:35:40.68,English,,0,0,0,,Restoring the Byzantine Empire.\N{\rChinese}恢复拜占庭帝国。
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.94,0:35:44.04,English,,0,0,0,,And thus unifying the Orthodox world.\N{\rChinese}于是统一正教世界。
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.42,0:35:50.68,English,,0,0,0,,After the United States leaves the Middle East,\N{\rChinese}美国离开中东后，大以色列计划化为以色列帝国。
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.38,0:35:56.10,English,,0,0,0,,the Greater Israel Project becomes the Empire of Israel.\N{\rChinese}the Greater Israel Project becomes the Empire of Israel.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.42,0:35:58.84,English,,0,0,0,,The Empire of Israel,\N{\rChinese}以色列帝国，
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.08,0:36:02.04,English,,0,0,0,,in order to restore the Davidic Kingdom,\N{\rChinese}为恢复大卫王国，
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.22,0:36:03.80,English,,0,0,0,,in order to usher in the Byzantine Age,\N{\rChinese}为迎来拜占庭时代，他们摧毁岩石穹顶以建造第三圣殿。
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.02,0:36:09.14,English,,0,0,0,,they destroy the Dome of the Rock to build the Third Temple.\N{\rChinese}他们摧毁岩石穹顶以建造第三圣殿。
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.16,0:36:15.24,English,,0,0,0,,This causes anti -Semitism to explode throughout the world.\N{\rChinese}这导致世界各地反犹太主义爆发。
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.32,0:36:19.26,English,,0,0,0,,Thus compelling Jews to return to Israel.\N{\rChinese}于是犹太人被迫返回以色列。
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.46,0:36:25.64,English,,0,0,0,,The entire Islamic world wants vengeance against Israel.\N{\rChinese}整个伊斯兰世界都想报复以色列。
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.16,0:36:28.90,English,,0,0,0,,But their leadership, their political elite,\N{\rChinese}但他们的领导层，他们的政治精英，
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.04,0:36:33.62,English,,0,0,0,,have been co -opted and compromised by the Anglo -American Empire and by the Israeli Empire.\N{\rChinese}已被英美帝国和以色列帝国兼并并妥协，
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.98,0:36:37.24,English,,0,0,0,,And so this forces revolutions and\N{\rChinese}于是这促成了革命与
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.24,0:36:40.94,English,,0,0,0,,civil conflict around the Islamic world. And\N{\rChinese}伊斯兰世界的内战。随后
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.94,0:36:44.92,English,,0,0,0,,now people are begging for\N{\rChinese}人们开始乞求
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.92,0:36:46.98,English,,0,0,0,,the Magni to return.\N{\rChinese}Magni归来。
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.16,0:36:51.22,English,,0,0,0,,The Magni is their world unifier.\N{\rChinese}马格尼是他们的世界统一者。
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.32,0:36:57.48,English,,0,0,0,,At this point, there are certain elements within the Islamic world\N{\rChinese}此时，伊斯兰世界中出现了若干要素
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.48,0:37:01.14,English,,0,0,0,,who see Putin as the great savior.\N{\rChinese}他们把普京视为伟大的救世主
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.82,0:37:04.40,English,,0,0,0,,And in the Islamic eschatology,\N{\rChinese}在伊斯兰末世论中，
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.68,0:37:08.04,English,,0,0,0,,the name for Putin\N{\rChinese}普京的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.04,0:37:11.12,English,,0,0,0,,is Dao Kanaan,\N{\rChinese}道坎安，
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.30,0:37:16.80,English,,0,0,0,,which is the same concept as the Orthodox idea of the catacomb.\N{\rChinese}这与正教关于地下墓穴的概念相同。
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.02,0:37:21.76,English,,0,0,0,,The one who stops the Antichrist from emerging. And so\N{\rChinese}停止反基督出现的人。于是
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.76,0:37:27.28,English,,0,0,0,,Putin will initiate reconciliation between the Islamic world\N{\rChinese}普京将启动伊斯兰世界的和解
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.28,0:37:30.40,English,,0,0,0,,and the Orthodox world. It will be an alliance between the Orthodox\N{\rChinese}并且与正教世界。它将是正教与伊斯兰世界的联盟。
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.40,0:37:32.22,English,,0,0,0,,and the Islamic world.\N{\rChinese}并且与正教世界。它将是正教与伊斯兰世界的联盟。
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.54,0:37:35.66,English,,0,0,0,,And at this point,\N{\rChinese}此时，
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.58,0:37:40.34,English,,0,0,0,,Putin, can now seek reconciliation\N{\rChinese}普京现在可以寻求和解
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.01,0:37:43.76,English,,0,0,0,,between the Islamic world\N{\rChinese}与伊斯兰世界
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.76,0:37:46.40,English,,0,0,0,,and the Israeli Empire.\N{\rChinese}与以色列帝国
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.66,0:37:50.16,English,,0,0,0,,He can also seek reconciliation between the Orthodox world\N{\rChinese}他也可以寻求与正教世界的和解
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.16,0:37:51.68,English,,0,0,0,,and the Catholic world.\N{\rChinese}以及天主教世界。
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.82,0:37:55.04,English,,0,0,0,,And thus unifying the world under him.\N{\rChinese}于是把世界统一在他之下。
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.32,0:37:59.96,English,,0,0,0,,So this is the framework of the world for the next 10 -20 years.\N{\rChinese}于是这就是未来10-20年世界的框架。
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.96,0:38:03.70,English,,0,0,0,,Now, do I think this will actually happen?\N{\rChinese}现在，我认为这会真的发生吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.94,0:38:08.28,English,,0,0,0,,Do I actually think that Putin will replace the Anglo -American Empire?\N{\rChinese}我真的认为普京会取代英美帝国吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.56,0:38:13.06,English,,0,0,0,,He thinks he will succeed.\N{\rChinese}他认为自己会成功。
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.24,0:38:16.56,English,,0,0,0,,But I don't think he will succeed. And the reason why is because he's human.\N{\rChinese}但我认为他不会成功，原因是他是人。
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.26,0:38:19.84,English,,0,0,0,,And once he dies, then\N{\rChinese}而当他去世后，
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.84,0:38:22.50,English,,0,0,0,,civil conflict will arise\N{\rChinese}内战将爆发
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.18,0:38:25.54,English,,0,0,0,,within this grand alliance. And\N{\rChinese}在这大联盟之内。然后
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.54,0:38:31.48,English,,0,0,0,,this civil conflict will lead to catastrophe after catastrophe after catastrophe.\N{\rChinese}这场内战将接连不断的灾祸。
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.62,0:38:34.58,English,,0,0,0,,It will be the age of tribulation. Many,\N{\rChinese}将是动荡之世。众多
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.70,0:38:37.82,English,,0,0,0,,many people will die in this age of tribulation.\N{\rChinese}许多人将在这动荡之世中相继逝去。
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.02,0:38:42.56,English,,0,0,0,,So the outlook for humanity is not that great.\N{\rChinese}因此，人类的前景并不算太好。
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.82,0:38:45.72,English,,0,0,0,,And this is no different from what happened\N{\rChinese}而这与公元650-600年左右发生的情况无异。
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.72,0:38:49.42,English,,0,0,0,,in about 650 -600 Common Era\N{\rChinese}在公元650-600年左右发生的情况与此无异。
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.42,0:38:52.64,English,,0,0,0,,when Muhammad was this great charismatic figure who\N{\rChinese}当穆罕默德是那位伟大的有魅力人物时，
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.64,0:38:55.54,English,,0,0,0,,was supposed to unite the entire world.\N{\rChinese}他本应统一全世界。
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.58,0:38:57.66,English,,0,0,0,,And he would have if he lived another 10 years.\N{\rChinese}他若再活十年，便会如此。
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.84,0:38:59.48,English,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, he died. And\N{\rChinese}不幸的是，他去世了。
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.48,0:39:04.26,English,,0,0,0,,this created civil conflict within the Muslim world.\N{\rChinese}这导致了穆斯林世界内部的内战。
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.46,0:39:07.48,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, so, those are my predictions.\N{\rChinese}好的，那就是我的预测。
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.80,0:39:09.20,English,,0,0,0,,And again, the thesis,\N{\rChinese}再说一次，论点是，
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.34,0:39:14.64,English,,0,0,0,,the grand idea is eschatology drives geopolitics.\N{\rChinese}大想法是，末世论驱动地缘政治。
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.72,0:39:17.88,English,,0,0,0,,So if things happen the way they do,\N{\rChinese}如果事情按预期发展，
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.16,0:39:19.96,English,,0,0,0,,then it's because of eschatology.\N{\rChinese}那就归因于末世论。
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.20,0:39:23.52,English,,0,0,0,,And that gives us proof, compelling proof\N{\rChinese}这给了我们充分的证明，足以证明。
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.52,0:39:27.80,English,,0,0,0,,that it's really eschatology that drives geopolitics.\N{\rChinese}那正是末世论驱动地缘政治。
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.92,0:39:30.08,English,,0,0,0,,So we'll see what happens in the next 10, 20 years.\N{\rChinese}接下来十、二十年会怎样，咱们拭目以待。
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.58,0:39:33.18,English,,0,0,0,,Now, having said all this,\N{\rChinese}说完这些，
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.86,0:39:35.48,English,,0,0,0,,I have to say, it's not\N{\rChinese}我得说，这不是……
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.40,0:39:39.68,English,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's not secret what I'm saying.\N{\rChinese}我的意思是，这不是我说的秘密。
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.90,0:39:42.86,English,,0,0,0,,It's not a great secret I've uncovered.\N{\rChinese}这不是我发现的大秘密。
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.28,0:39:48.36,English,,0,0,0,,I mean, if you read Alexander Dugin, he lays out this plan coherently in his interviews\N{\rChinese}我说的是，如果你读过亚历山大·杜金，他在访谈中和书里都把这个计划说得很连贯
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.36,0:39:51.16,English,,0,0,0,,and in his books. So then the question then is,\N{\rChinese}于是问题来了，
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.28,0:39:54.10,English,,0,0,0,,given that this is public domain knowledge,\N{\rChinese}既然这已是公开知识，
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.48,0:39:57.04,English,,0,0,0,,why doesn't the Anglo -American Empire\N{\rChinese}为什么英美帝国没有……
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.90,0:40:02.00,English,,0,0,0,,respond strategically to this?\N{\rChinese}回应战略性吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.42,0:40:05.56,English,,0,0,0,,Why doesn't the Anglo -American Empire have countermeasures\N{\rChinese}英美帝国为什么没有反制措施？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.56,0:40:08.44,English,,0,0,0,,and counter strategies Why isn't the Anglo -American Empire\N{\rChinese}以及反制策略，英美帝国为何不着手自保？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.14,0:40:11.70,English,,0,0,0,,intent on its own self -preservation?\N{\rChinese}它们的意图是自保吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.94,0:40:14.68,English,,0,0,0,,And the answer is\N{\rChinese}答案是
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.30,0:40:17.40,English,,0,0,0,,because the people who control the Anglo -American Empire\N{\rChinese}因为掌控英美帝国的人
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.44,0:40:19.80,English,,0,0,0,,today don't care.\N{\rChinese}他们今天不在乎。
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.92,0:40:23.86,English,,0,0,0,,Because they'll be dead in 10, 20, 30 years time.\N{\rChinese}因为他们十、二十、三十年后就会去世。
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.40,0:40:28.40,English,,0,0,0,,All they want to do until they die is enjoy their life.\N{\rChinese}他们只想在去世前享受人生。
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.54,0:40:33.18,English,,0,0,0,,And they don't care what will happen to the world after their death.\N{\rChinese}他们不在乎自己去世后世界会怎样。
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.38,0:40:35.40,English,,0,0,0,,These people, of course, are called the baby boomers.\N{\rChinese}这些人，当然被称为婴儿潮人。
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.40,0:40:39.30,English,,0,0,0,,They're the ones who control all the political power, the financial power,\N{\rChinese}他们是掌握所有政治权力、金融权力的人。
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.46,0:40:45.38,English,,0,0,0,,the influential power in America,\N{\rChinese}美国的影响力
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.54,0:40:48.78,English,,0,0,0,,the cultural power in America and in the West today.\N{\rChinese}美国和今天西方的文化力量
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.94,0:40:51.94,English,,0,0,0,,And that's why the West is dying.\N{\rChinese}于是西方才会衰亡。
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.20,0:40:55.38,English,,0,0,0,,So I'm going to talk about this topic in my next video.\N{\rChinese}我将在下一段视频里谈此题。
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.54,0:40:58.90,English,,0,0,0,,So I look forward to seeing everyone then.\N{\rChinese}我期待届时与大家相见。
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.58,0:41:05.52,English,,0,0,0,,If you're interested, please join my Discord server.\N{\rChinese}如果你感兴趣，请加入我的 Discord 服务器。
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.70,0:41:07.52,English,,0,0,0,,I'm going to put the link below. If you're the means,\N{\rChinese}我会把链接放在下面。若你有时间，
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.82,0:41:11.82,English,,0,0,0,,please support my work by donating to\N{\rChinese}请通过捐款支持我的工作。
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.82,0:41:13.86,English,,0,0,0,,me on Buy Me A Coffee.\N{\rChinese}在 Buy Me A Coffee上给我打赏。
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.10,0:41:16.64,English,,0,0,0,,I really appreciate all the donations.\N{\rChinese}我非常感谢所有的捐款。
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.84,0:41:20.56,English,,0,0,0,,It's real validation of my work.\N{\rChinese}这是真正对我的工作的肯定。
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.78,0:41:22.96,English,,0,0,0,,Okay. All right. So thank you so much.\N{\rChinese}好的。好了。非常感谢。
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.96,0:41:24.90,English,,0,0,0,,And I will see everyone next week.\N{\rChinese}下周见。
